This is becoming a next generation TaskJuggler IDE for KDE.


Current features:
- (flat) task list
- (tree) resource list
- Gantt chart (with task dependencies)
- sorting
- quick search bar for searching and filtering the listviews
- resource usage view
- project source editor
- report view (task coverage, resource usage)


Planned features:
- storable filters

For the complete list, see:
http://www.taskjuggler.org/ide.php
